## 5. Kebutuhan Non-Fungsional

### 5.1 Performa

| Metrik | Target | Cara Pengukuran |
|:---|:---|:---|
| Time to Interactive (TTI) | < 3 detik | Lighthouse |
| Waktu proses transaksi | < 1 detik (dari klik bayar hingga struk siap) | Custom metrics |
| Response time API | < 200ms (P95) | APM monitoring |
| Concurrent users | 100+ per outlet | Load testing |
| Database query time | < 50ms (P95) | Query profiling |
| Uptime | 99.9% (8.76 jam downtime/tahun) | Monitoring |

### 5.2 Keamanan

| Aspek | Implementasi |
|:---|:---|
| Enkripsi data transit | TLS 1.3 (HTTPS) |
| Enkripsi data at rest | AES-256 untuk data sensitif |
| Password hashing | bcrypt dengan salt |
| Session management | JWT + refresh token, auto-expire |
| Rate limiting | Throttle API 100 req/min per user |
| Input validation | Sanitize semua input, parameterized queries |
| Audit trail | Log semua operasi sensitif (delete, edit harga, void) |
| OWASP Top 10 | Mitigasi XSS, CSRF, SQL Injection, dll. |

### 5.3 Skalabilitas

| Aspek | Strategi |
|:---|:---|
| Horizontal scaling | Stateless API, load balancer |
| Database scaling | Read replicas, connection pooling |
| Caching | Redis untuk session & frequently accessed data |
| CDN | Static assets via CDN (Vercel Edge) |
| Multi-tenancy | Tenant isolation via database schema |

### 5.4 Aksesibilitas & UX

| Aspek | Implementasi |
|:---|:---|
| Responsive design | Optimal di desktop (1024px+), tablet (768px+), mobile (360px+) |
| Touch-friendly | Minimum tap target 44x44px |
| Kontras warna | WCAG 2.1 AA compliance |
| Bahasa | Bahasa Indonesia (default), English (opsional) |
| Onboarding | Wizard setup bisnis pertama kali + tooltip panduan |
| Loading states | Skeleton loader, progress indicator |
| Error handling | User-friendly error messages + retry option |

